'''Chrissie England''' was the Visual Effects Executive Producer of [[Industrial Light & Magic]] for [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''The Phantom Menace'']]. She was also a member of the Administrative Staff for [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']].

She had a small cameo in the theatrical release of ''The Phantom Menace'', as a [[Human/Legends|Human]] member of [[Orn Free Taa/Legends|Orn Free Taa's]] delegation in the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]]. However, the character was replaced with a [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] [[Orn Free Taa's Twi'lek aide|aide]] for the DVD release.

In February [[2006]], she along with [[George Lucas]] was awarded a National Medal of Science and Technology by United States President George W. Bush, for ILM's technological innovations.
